OL,3,CSir Richard Branson's wife Joan dies
OL,4,Caged 80
OL,6,FSir Richard Branson has announced the
OL,7,Fdeath of his wife, Lady Joan, after 50
OL,8,Fyears together.
OL,10,FIn a statement on social media on
OL,11,FTuesday, the Virgin founder said:
OL,12,F"Heartbroken to share that Joan, my
OL,13,Fwife and partner for 50 years, has
OL,14,Fpassed away.
OL,16,F"She was the most wonderful mum and
OL,17,Fgrandmum our kids and grandkids could
OL,18,Fhave ever wished for.
OL,20,F"She was my best friend, my rock, my
OL,21,Fguiding light, my world.
