OL,6,F"Love you forever, Joan x."
OL,8,FLady Joan, with whom Sir Richard
OL,9,Fshared two children, has long been
OL,10,Fcredited as his greatest source of
OL,11,Fsupport and wisdom.
OL,13,FJust last week, he had posted a photo
OL,14,Fof himself kissing her head, writing:
OL,15,F"Everyone needs a Joan in their life."
