OL,3,CSir Richard Branson's wife Joan dies
OL,4,Caged 80
OL,6,FShe was believed to be in good health
OL,7,Fwhen she celebrated her 80th birthday
OL,8,Fthis summer, with Sir Richard paying
OL,9,Ftribute at the time to her constant
OL,10,Fpresence "through the highs, the lows,
OL,11,Fand all those quiet, content and
OL,12,Fpeaceful moments in between".
OL,14,FIn an article written for the Virgin
OL,15,Fwebsite celebrating her 70th birthday,
OL,16,Fthe entrepreneur previously said he
OL,17,Ffell in love with Ms Templeman "from
OL,18,Fthe first moment I saw her" as she
OL,19,Fworked in a bric-a-brac shop in
OL,20,FLondon's Westbourne Grove.
