OL,7,F"persistently hang around the shop and
OL,8,Fbuy countless objects", including an
OL,9,Fold advertising sign, before the pair
OL,10,Fstarted to date.
OL,12,FIn the piece, the businessman said his
OL,13,Fwife was a "very private person" who
OL,14,Fhad "always stood by me mentally,
OL,15,Femotionally and spiritually".
